# Format:
# <app>: <type>: <short description>
#
# Apps:
# Main
# Event_Tracker
# Blog_Posts
# Recipes
# Photo_Album
#
# Types:
# feat     New feature
# fix      Bug fix
# refactor Code change without behavior change
# test     Tests added/updated
# chore    Maintenance (gems, configs)
# docs     Documentation only
# style    Formatting, linting
# perf     Performance improvements
# build    CI/CD, dependencies
# revert   Reverting a commit
#
# Rules:
# - Use EXACT app names above
# - Use EXACT types above
# - Description must be at least 10 characters
# - Use tabs between sections
#
# Example:
# Blog_Posts:	feat:	Add pagination to index page
#
# Write your commit below:
